title: cervical cancer tissue/cells (A101_Ce36)
extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol extraction of total RNA was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol from 6 ug total RNA (Expression Analysis Technical Manual, 2001, Affymetrix).
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 10 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on GeneChip Drosophila Genome Array. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 400.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Hewlett-Packard GeneArray Scanner G2500A.
description: Gene expression data from cervical carcinoma tissue/cells
data_processing: The data were analyzed with R/Bioconductor RMA algorithm. Data were log2 transformed
